Ingredients
2 red capsicum
4 tablespoon Extra Virgin Olive Oil
120 g toasted walnuts
1 garlic clove roughly chopped
2 ½ tablespoon tomato paste
¾ cup bread crumbs
2 tablespoon pomegranate molasses
1 teaspoon Aleppo pepper
½ teaspoon sugar
1 teaspoon sumac
½ teaspoon salt
½ teaspoon cayenne pepper






Method
Brush red capsicum with olive oil and roast in oven for 30 min at 225 C

Remove into a bowl and cover to allow to steam

After cooled, peel and cut into thin strips

Mix along with the rest of the ingredients in a mixer until smooth




